Introducing this series to torrents in a small file size. There is a wiki for this series with many details. In these fileshares I will not repeat a lot of that.

From the wiki

Johnny Staccato is an American private detective series starring John Cassavetes which ran for 27 episodes on NBC from September 10, 1959 through March 24, 1960.

"The Return" 	December 17, 1959 	A Korean War veteran, suspicious of his wife over imagined affairs, escapes from a mental hospital and is intent on killing her.

  One thing about doing this series is the discovery of actors with long distinguised caeers who you may not know.  Tom Reese is one of these.  Full info at IMDb.
